www.esnips.com &lt;http://www.esnips.com/&gt; 



Here is my account so you can get a feel for how it works..



My link to all my folders:

http://www.esnips.com/FoldersAction.ns



In case that doesn&#39;t work here is a link to a specific folder - April 2009
to be exact:

http://www.esnips.com/web/ckmorris95-April2009



Let me know if you need further help.

Kristin





