To: EVP-ITC@yahoogroups .com
Subject: Re: [EVP-ITC] File uploading rules





Ok, Misty I&#39;ll take them out, this recording stuff is new to me.

In a message dated 5/10/2009 1:13:01 A.M. Eastern Daylight Time,
bulletbabea@ yahoo.com writes:


Please do not upload wav format files here they will have to be removed. Our
group only has a very limited amount of space. Upload bigger files and mass
amount of files to your esnips.com accounts or elsewhere to be shared here
using links. 

Misty

